          <title>Feeling lucky? Jackpot for Mega Millions climbs to more than $1 billion</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Hang onto those stocking-stuffer lottery tickets. The Mega Millions jackpot has surpassed $1 billion after no ticket matched all six numbers drawn on Christmas Eve. That means the estimated jackpot for Friday's drawing is $1.15 billion, potentially the fifth-largest jackpot in the game's history.]]></description>
